James M. Loree 
Executive Compensation
As President and CEO at STANLEY BLACK & DECKER INC, James M. Loree  made $11,425,513 in total compensation.  Of this total $992,500 was received as a salary, $1,615,320 was received as a bonus, $4,757,251 was received in stock options, $3,833,202 was awarded as stock and $227,240 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


